name: Ethereum Bridged NEDX from BNB
description: ETH.n represents the Ethereum-denominated asset within the NEDX ecosystem, optimized for smooth usage across decentralized applications. ETH.n is intended for swaps, liquidity pools, trading pairs, and broader ecosystem utility, offering a consistent asset representation for Ethereum-based value inside NEDX. It supports rapid transfers, efficient settlement, and interoperable usage across dApps, making it suitable for both active trading and long-term ecosystem participation.
